    <item>
      <title>Request: Harmshield AA</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Necromancers&amp;message.id=9831#M9831</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;Harmshield as an AA would be a big help to raiding Necros. Necros have the ability to save raids with their Feign Death AA. Unfortunately this often leaves the necro in a spot near mobs that will agro when they stand up. The instant invis AA works much of the time when a Necro is soloing or grouping to get away from mobs after being FD. Most raid targets have a lot of see invis mobs around so it does not work in that situation. Harmshiled would allow a Necro to possibly get to a safe spot before feigning again but most of us don't have that spell memmed most of the time. Harmshield as an expansion AA would solve the problem. This would allow a feigned Necro to stand up, click the Harmshield AA and then train away the mobs and/or get to a safe spot to feign again. It would not be overpowering since we already have this ability as a spell currently. It would just make it more accessible. A one hour reuse timer would be about right (presuming your raid does not wipe more often than that).&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
